title: Eurostar on alert as Paris grapples with bed bug infestation
description: Eurostar staff are on alert due to a bed bug infestation in Paris, which has hit the French capital in recent days.

title: US hands Ukraine more than a million rounds of ammunition it seized from Iranian ship
description: The United States has sent over a million rounds of ammunition it seized from an Iranian ship last December to Ukraine.

title: 'Ghastly' Venice bus crash leaves unanswered questions as tourist city mourns 'unbearable tragedy'
description: We are standing on the side of a flyover, looking over the edge, and it is a fearful sight.

title: Teen girl 'in coma' after 'attack by Iranian police for not wearing hijab'
description: A teenage girl is in a coma after she was "physically attacked" by Iranian authorities for not wearing a hijab, according to a human rights group.

title: 'Dozens of cats' found abandoned in Abu Dhabi desert as authorities launch investigation
description: Authorities in Abu Dhabi are investigating reports of cats being abandoned in the desert, with dozens said to have died.

title: FIFA World Cup to be hosted in six countries across three continents in 2030
description: The 2030 men's FIFA World Cup is set to be spread across six countries on three continents, world football's governing body has said.

title: Warming world nearing 'point of no return', says Pope Francis
description: Pope Francis has appealed to world leaders to address climate change before it's too late, warning the planet is nearing a "point of no return".

title: FIFA considering lifting blanket ban on Russia competing in international football
description: FIFA is looking at ending Russia's blanket ban from international football, Sky News understands.

title: China appears to censor image of athletes embracing after unintended Tiananmen Square reference
description: A picture showing two female Chinese athletes which makes an unintentional reference to the Tiananmen Square massacre appears to have been censored on social media in China.

title: Five big revelations from the new Beckham Netflix documentary
description: A new documentary delves into the life of David Beckham - half of one of the world's most photographed and iconic couples.

title: UK and Ireland set to host Euro 2028
description: The UK and Ireland bid to host Euro 2028 is now unopposed after UEFA announced Turkey's decision to withdraw from the process.

title: Ronaldo's rape accuser to revive legal challenge over hush money deal
description: Lawyers representing football star Cristiano Ronaldo are set to return to court today in a legal battle over the hush money he paid in 2010 to a woman who accused him of raping her.
